GeneralComments: Free! There are 34 powered sites, and you're welcome to charge here thanks to the generosity of Ken Ryan. Email him on Info@greytowncampground.co.nz while charging to say "thanks, just letting you I've charged today at the campground" so he can track usage. You can also charge as an overnight paying guest. Gates open between 730am-930pm. Awesome kids playground at gate.
